<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
	<title></title>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<style type="text/css">
		@@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.background-blue{
				width: 100% !important;
				padding: 0;
			}			
			.wrapper{
				height: 20rem !important;
			}
			.wrapper div{
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
			}			
		}
		
		.container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
			height: 100%;
		}
		h2 img{
			height: 3rem;
		}

		.title {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			gap:.5rem;
			width: 60%;
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			text-align: center;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			padding-bottom: 10px;
			border-bottom: 3px solid #ffffff;
		}

		.button {
			display: block;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			max-width: 110px;
			background-color: #007bff;
			color: #fff;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
			font-size: 18px;
			cursor: pointer;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			text-decoration: none;
		}
		.button:hover{
			filter: brightness(.9);
		}
		
		.description {
			display: flex;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			text-align: center;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			padding-bottom: 10px;
			
		}
		.background-blue { 
			width: 50%;
		}
		.wrapper{
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			height: 31.25rem;
			justify-content: space-between;
			background-color: #f7f5f5 ;
		}
		.header{
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			background-color: #023163b7;
			padding: 1rem 0;
			width: 100%;
			color: #f7f5f5;
		}
		.content{
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="background-blue">

			<div class="wrapper">
				<div class="header">
					<h2 class="title"> <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/GpfX6zsc/android-chrome-256x256.png" alt=""> MundoWeb</h2>	
					<div class="description">Recuperação de Senha </div>	
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<h4>Olá @Model.Nome </h4>
					<p>Recebemos sua solicitação de mudança de senha no <strong>Mundo Web</strong></p>
					<p>Clique no botão abaixo para criar uma nova senha</p>
					<a href="@Model.Url/alterar-senha?codigo=@Model.Codigo" class="button">Alterar senha</a>
					<p>Lembrando que o link tem validade de @Model.ExpiracaoEmHoras horas desde o pedido de troca da senha.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>